nodes.text: David Rabbitte (b. January 23, 1970) is an artist who drew the illustrations for the short stories Roll of the Dice in Star Wars Insider 135 and The Last Battle of Colonel Jace Malcom in Star Wars Insider 137. He also drew the cover illustration for Abel G. Peña's eNovella SkyeWalkers: A Clone Wars Story.
David has also been part of many of Topps' card sets, including illustrating base card art for multiple Galaxy Series sets.
